Lingua-DE-TypoGenerator version 0.2
===================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DESCRIPTION

Lingua::DE::TypoGenerator will generate a list of possible typos for a
given word. It uses a German keyboard layout and aims to be the German
counterpart to Lingua::TypoGenerator.

